Invocation Name: shady tree
des: A skill that enables scheduling of Landscaping and Fall clean up services for your residential or commercial properties in Massachusetts, Rhode Island and Southern New Hampshire. Our mission here at Shady Tree Landscaping & Irrigation is to be the leader in outdoor maintenance by listening to our customers and delivering services that exceeds their expectations. Our Alexa skill allows you to contact us about fall cleanups by simply saying rake my leaves.
